{"tid":493795,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"事主錯認「軍佬」為「未來戰士」","createTime":"2017-12-09T02:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T02:38:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6697f2d65028a04117471654d8c68e48f893de3b","tid":493795,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:24:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171209/20239218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F20239218&d=aAykAqn9Fjiz0GAmjPOR9L5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=2d4888f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F20239218&h=951c3da7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171209/20239218</a><br />\n<br />\n事主錯認「軍佬」為「未來戰士」<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【宅男被毆案】<br />\n【本報訊】網名「司徒奈奈」的宅男屢問女網友「扑唔扑嘢」，被拒便於網上唱衰對方，遭設局誘出圍毆兼拍片一案續審。庭上透露因裝扮被司徒奈奈稱呼為「未來戰士」的第三被告溫穎賢，原來案發日他是cosplay遊戲《街頭霸王》內「軍佬」一角。<br />\n<br />\n溫的口供指，去年2月14日應首被告「玲瓏」陳顯華邀約到九展出席cosplay展，陳稱要教訓在網上騷擾女coser的司徒奈奈，其間他有打事主羅浩峰，施以掌摑、踢膝和拳打，後來他見事主遭「肥仔」踢鼻，他想阻止卻被震開。但他稱沒搶事主財物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171209/large/09ls3p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171209%2Flarge%2F09ls3p3.jpg&h=87c206cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n溫穎賢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5被告表證成立<br />\n<br />\n第四被告「肥仔」曾栢豪的口供否認向事主施襲，只鬧過對方；第五被告「皮褸」趙文俊則承認打過事主，並搶走他80元買電話叉電插頭。法官昨接納次被告「白毛」邵頌然申請，不接納控方將其口頭招認及筆錄口供呈堂，又裁定5被告表證成立，各人不自辯，案件下周一作結案陳詞。<br />\n案件編號：DCCC418/17<br />\n■記者蔡少玲"},{"pid":"9472e1e113098a6130875d9ab66b662a8b67e2d3","tid":493795,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:29:09.000Z","msg":"仲有幾多野可以柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0185f213984508473dd41e1ca7dc92b2b862e1d","tid":493795,"uid":61094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:33:44.000Z","msg":"呢個唔好笑，追星族都唔會認得哂所有明星啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d06ca377f5d6398b2f3399d6e9d09b4418d4cf","tid":493795,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i4/388009063/T2eWIoXUxXXXXXXXXX-388009063.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi4%2F388009063%2FT2eWIoXUxXXXXXXXXX-388009063.jpg&h=76fcb6b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n軍佬"},{"pid":"d83b66a8dc2f8db0d539d65bcd51d159be69d392","tid":493795,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i4/388009063/T2eWIoXUxXXXXXXXXX-388009063.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi4%2F388009063%2FT2eWIoXUxXXXXXXXXX-388009063.jpg&h=76fcb6b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n軍佬</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170405/photo/bkn-20170405071534940-0405_00862_001_01p.jpg?20170405072459\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170405%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170405071534940-0405_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20170405072459&h=d69c01bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n未來戰士"},{"pid":"3cfbfd39f7c1f7cd6df2fe6a1515cfba5e758a62","tid":493795,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i4/388009063/T2eWIoXUxXXXXXXXXX-388009063.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fi